[
  {
    "text": "- Do you have advice for young minds today",
    "start": "1880",
    "end": "3800"
  },
  {
    "text": "dreaming about, creating\nas you have dreamt,",
    "start": "3800",
    "end": "7210"
  },
  {
    "text": "creating intelligence systems?",
    "start": "7210",
    "end": "9290"
  },
  {
    "text": "What is the best way to arrive\nat new breakthrough ideas",
    "start": "9290",
    "end": "12800"
  },
  {
    "text": "and carry them through\nthe fire of criticism",
    "start": "12800",
    "end": "15350"
  },
  {
    "text": "and past conventional ideas?",
    "start": "16450",
    "end": "18433"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ask your questions.",
    "start": "20190",
    "end": "21240"
  },
  {
    "text": "Really, your questions are never dumb.",
    "start": "24520",
    "end": "28053"
  },
  {
    "text": "(laughs)",
    "start": "29045",
    "end": "29878"
  },
  {
    "text": "And so is your own way",
    "start": "29878",
    "end": "30978"
  },
  {
    "text": "and don't take no for an answer.",
    "start": "32090",
    "end": "34432"
  },
  {
    "text": "(chuckles)",
    "start": "34432",
    "end": "36510"
  },
  {
    "text": "If they're really dumb,\nyou will find out quickly,",
    "start": "36510",
    "end": "39789"
  },
  {
    "text": "by trial and error,",
    "start": "39790",
    "end": "41280"
  },
  {
    "text": "to see that they're not leading any place.",
    "start": "41280",
    "end": "43379"
  },
  {
    "text": "But, follow them and try to\nunderstand things your way.",
    "start": "45227",
    "end": "50227"
  },
  {
    "text": "That is my advice.",
    "start": "50860",
    "end": "53000"
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know if it's gonna help anyone.",
    "start": "53000",
    "end": "55390"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Interviewer] No,\nthat's brilliantly put.",
    "start": "55390",
    "end": "57833"
  },
  {
    "text": "- There is a lot of",
    "start": "57833",
    "end": "58730"
  },
  {
    "text": "inertia",
    "start": "61446",
    "end": "62629"
  },
  {
    "text": "in science, in academia.",
    "start": "63530",
    "end": "65603"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is slowing down science.",
    "start": "66570",
    "end": "68873"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Interviewer] Yeah\nthose two words: your way,",
    "start": "69980",
    "end": "72730"
  },
  {
    "text": "that's a powerful thing.",
    "start": "72730",
    "end": "74444"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's against inertia, potentially.",
    "start": "74444",
    "end": "77510"
  },
  {
    "text": "Against the full,",
    "start": "77510",
    "end": "78410"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Older Man] Against your professor.",
    "start": "78410",
    "end": "80290"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Against your professor.\n(laughs)",
    "start": "80290",
    "end": "81880"
  },
  {
    "text": "- I wrote a book of why,",
    "start": "81880",
    "end": "83719"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Interviewer] Yeah.",
    "start": "83720",
    "end": "84553"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order to democratize common sense.",
    "start": "84553",
    "end": "87260"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Interviewer] Yeah.",
    "start": "87260",
    "end": "88234"
  },
  {
    "text": "(both laugh)",
    "start": "88234",
    "end": "90110"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order to instill,",
    "start": "90110",
    "end": "93050"
  },
  {
    "text": "rebellious spirits in students.",
    "start": "93050",
    "end": "96820"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, they wouldn't wait until\nthe professor get things right.",
    "start": "96820",
    "end": "101755"
  },
  {
    "text": "(both laugh)",
    "start": "101755",
    "end": "104172"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Interviewer] So,\nyou wrote the manifesto",
    "start": "105090",
    "end": "106386"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"The Rebellion Against the Professor\".",
    "start": "106387",
    "end": "109520"
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Older Man] Against the professor, yes.",
    "start": "109520",
    "end": "110473"
  }
]